We shimmied around this problem by comparing different sources with different kinds of values and using different mass calculations
様々な出典や様々な種類の値
様々な質量計算を使用し

154
00:12:44,317 --> 00:12:51,120
 to arrive at a standardized list that allowed us to be as accurate as humanly possible.
可能な限り正確なリストを
作ることでこの問題に取り組んだつもりですが

155
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:53,539
You can look at all of this in our source doc.
これらは全て概要欄から確認できます

156
